➜开源网络访问控制系统PacketFence 3.0版发布
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=26134	8880
开源网络访问控制系统<a href="http://packetfence.org/">PacketFence</a>发布了<a href="https://lwn.net/Articles/460062/">3.0版</a>（<a href="http://www.packetfence.org/tour/screenshots.html">屏幕截图</a>）。<i>
